Comment.val: /*Export program to export GIOM information to IPS payments.*/

ExpSyntax.val: 'Er is een onherstelbare fout opgetreden. Gegevens worden teruggerold. !'

SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT tpab.tr_id, ips_re_id, mutaties.amount, mutaties.entrydate, mutaties.valuedate, ips_rekeningnummer, ips_weergave_debet_positief, ips_exac_id, ips_nostro_exac_id, re_nummer, re_muntsoort, tr_transnummer, tr_rel1, tr_instruktie, tr_rel2, tr_rel2_rek2, tr_rel2_instructie, tr_symbool, tr_optietype, tr_expiratiedatum, tr_exerciseprijs, tr_indicatie, tr_transdatum, tr_ref_symbool, tr_herkomst_code_tr, tr_tprf_relatie, tr_tprf_instructie, tr_mut_gemaakt, tr_origtr_storno, to_omschrijving1 FROM tap_post_action_batch tpab INNER JOIN transactions t ON t.tr_volgnummer = tpab.tr_id INNER JOIN ( SELECT pmg_tr_volgnummer AS tr_id, pmg_re_id AS re_id, pmg_mutatie_aantal AS amount, pmg_boekdatum AS entrydate, pmg_valutadatum AS valuedate FROM positiemutaties_geld UNION ALL SELECT transaction_id AS tr_id, account_id AS re_id, amount AS amount, to_char(book_date, 'YYYYMMDD') AS entrydate, to_char(value_date, 'YYYYMMDD') AS valuedate FROM bank_cash_balance_mutations ) mutaties on mutaties.tr_id = tpab.tr_id INNER JOIN ips_instell_per_rek ips ON ips.ips_re_id = mutaties.re_id INNER JOIN rekeningen r ON r.re_id = ips.ips_re_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN trans_omschrijving tom ON tom.to_transactievolgnr = mutaties.tr_id WHERE bitand(tpab.post_action,128) = 128 AND mutaties.amount <> 0 AND NOT EXISTS (select 1 from TRANS_EXPORT where TE_TR_VOLGNUMMER = tpab.tr_id and TE_RE_ID = mutaties.re_id and TE_EXPORTSOORT = ~1 ) AND ips_totaliseren = 0 AND ips_relatienummer BETWEEN ~2 and ~3 AND ips_exac_id IS NOT NULL AND ips_nostro_exac_id IS NOT NULL AND tr_mut_gemaakt <> 'S'

SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT tpab.tr_id, ips_re_id, mutaties.amount, mutaties.entrydate, mutaties.valuedate, ips_relatienummer, ips_rekeningnummer, ips_weergave_debet_positief, ips_totaliseren, ips_exac_id, ips_nostro_exac_id, re_nummer, re_muntsoort, tr_symbool, tr_optietype, tr_expiratiedatum, tr_exerciseprijs, tr_indicatie, tr_transdatum, tr_ref_symbool, tr_herkomst_code_tr, tr_mut_gemaakt, tr_origtr_storno, to_omschrijving1 FROM tap_post_action_batch tpab INNER JOIN transactions t ON t.tr_volgnummer = tpab.tr_id INNER JOIN ( SELECT pmg_tr_volgnummer AS tr_id, pmg_re_id AS re_id, pmg_mutatie_aantal AS amount, pmg_boekdatum AS entrydate, pmg_valutadatum AS valuedate FROM positiemutaties_geld UNION ALL SELECT transaction_id AS tr_id, account_id AS re_id, amount AS amount, to_char(book_date, 'YYYYMMDD') AS entrydate, to_char(value_date, 'YYYYMMDD') AS valuedate FROM bank_cash_balance_mutations ) mutaties on mutaties.tr_id = tpab.tr_id INNER JOIN ips_instell_per_rek ips ON ips.ips_re_id = mutaties.re_id INNER JOIN rekeningen r ON r.re_id = ips.ips_re_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN trans_omschrijving tom ON tom.to_transactievolgnr = mutaties.tr_id WHERE bitand(tpab.post_action,128) = 128 AND mutaties.amount <> 0 AND NOT EXISTS (select 1 from TRANS_EXPORT where TE_TR_VOLGNUMMER = tpab.tr_id and TE_RE_ID = mutaties.re_id and TE_EXPORTSOORT = ~5 ) AND ips_totaliseren BETWEEN ~3 and ~4 AND ips_relatienummer BETWEEN ~1 and ~2 AND ips_exac_id IS NOT NULL AND ips_nostro_exac_id IS NOT NULL AND tr_mut_gemaakt <> 'S'
